feed.title: All Things Iconic
feed.subtitle: All Things Iconic is your one stop destination for today's hot topics. Each week, Jenna Naphtali takes you through the world of pop culture and well, whatever else is on her mind. Stay tuned for special guests, fun games, and a whole lot of laughs. Be sure to listen every Tuesday, it's going to be iconic.

entry.title: The Kardashians: The New Wave - Season 1 Episode 13

link.title: The Kardashians: The New Wave - Season 1 Episode 13

entry.content:
The long (emphasis on long) awaited Season 1 finale is here. What’s more iconic than ending the season off strong with the Kardashians? Jenna brings on the creator of High Tops Media, Gavin Berger to gab about The Kardashians on Hulu. While Gavin may not be the biggest Karjenner Stan out there (unlike Jenna), he sure has a lot to say.

Don’t forget to follow on Instagram!

entry.title: Off to LA - Season 1 Episode 8
entry.content:
In order to prep for her semester in Los Angeles, Jenna turns to Gerald, her friend and fellow Ithaca College student, who recently returned from his semester in LA. He shares his wildest stories, explains what it’s like being an LA transplant, and answers the question Jenna has been dying to know: Is Saddle Ranch really worth the hype?

entry.title: A Kardashian Kristmas - Season 1 Episode 6
entry.content:
As a Jew, Christmas for Jenna means Chinese food and stalking the Kardashians’ social media. It’s a known fact (or a Jenna fact) that nobody does Christmas better than the Kardashians. Jenna brings on her friend Sydney to discuss the glamorous Kardashians and admire the elaborate ways they celebrate Christmas. Bible, it’s a great episode.
